[01:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'one. So, every time that you upload something, it, you know, it creates a tag for it. Uh, just entering the location and taking a seat at the bar, generating this, we end up with an output like this. And what\'s important to note here is that this isn\'t'

